            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Anni ab incarnacione Domini nostri Iesu
                        Christi millesimo CXV, quartodecimo die intereuntes mense indicioone VIII.
                            <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Mansi"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001"><rs key="#Monasteries">Monesterio</rs>
                            Sancti Benedicti fundato iusta fluvium quod dicitur Lairone</orgName>
                        ubi nunc domnus <rs key="#Abbots">abas</rs>
                        <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/2189">Albericus</persName>
                        preordinato esse videtur. Ego <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #childOf #siblingOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Mansi #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3533">Fulco</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis</rs>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> cuiusdam <persName key="#parentOf #Lombard"
                            ref="#people/3534">Azonis</persName> profesus sum legem vivere <rs
                            key="#Lombard">Langobardorum</rs> offertor et donator ipsius monesterio
                        presens presentibus dixi: Quisquis in sanctis ac venerabilis locis in suis
                        aliquit contulerit rebus iusta auctoris vocem in oc seculo centuplum
                        accipiam, insuper quod mellius est vitam posidebit eternam. Ideoque ego qui
                        supra Fulco marchio dono et offero in eodem monesterio a presenti die eo
                        ordine ut subter legitur pro anime Azonis marchionis genitori meo et
                            <persName key="#Countess #parentOf #Testamentum" ref="#people/3535"
                            >Garsenda</persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitisaa</rs>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">genitrice</rs> mea et <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #Lombard" ref="#people/3536">Ugo</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germano</rs> meo et pro anima mea mercedem, idest <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">petia una de terra</rs> iuris mei quam ego
                        abere et possiderec visus sum super <placeName key="#Rivers"><rs
                                key="#Rivers">fluvium</rs> Adesis</placeName>, quidem petia ipsa de
                        terra <rs key="#Mansi">mansos</rs> XX in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Rivers #Canals" ref="#places/2983">Costa</placeName>;
                        coerit ei: ab uno latere fluvium Adesis, ab alio latere <placeName
                            key="#Canals"><rs key="#Canals">fossa</rs> quae dicitur
                            Gaibo</placeName>, ab uno capite poleseno, de supto de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2984">Ramedelo</placeName>, ab alio latere albaro de
                        Plobegano. Quae autem suprascripta petia de terra una cum accesione et
                        ingresione seu cum superioribus et inferioribus suis qualiter supra legitur
                        in integrum ab ac die in eodern monesterio Sancti Benedicti eadem terra ut
                        supra legitur dono et offero et per presentem <rs key="#Offersio/donatio"
                            >cartulam offersionis</rs> ibidem ad abendum confirmo, faciendum exinde
                        abas vel monachis qui pro tempore in eodem monesterio ordinati et Deo
                        deservierint ad eorum usu et sumptu eo ordine ut subter legitur pro anime
                        nostre mercedem. Quidem et spondeo atque promitto me ego qui supra Fulco
                        marchio una cum meos heredes a parte ipsius monasterii suprascripta petia de
                        terra qualiter supra decernitur in integrum ab omni omine defensare; quod si
                        defendere non potuerimus aut cui pars ipsi dederit per covis ingenium
                        subtraere quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> eadem terra a
                        parte ipsius monesterio restituamus, sicut pro tempore fuerit meliorata aut
                        valuerit sub estimatione in consimile loco. Hanc enim cartulam offersionem
                        pagina <persName key="#Notary #Writer #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Adam/notarius">Adam</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> tradidi et scribere rogavi in qua ic supter
                        confirmans <rs key="#Witness">testibus</rs> obtuli ad roborandum. Actum in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/912">Montagnania</placeName> feliciter. Signum
                        + manibus Fulco marchio qui anc cartulam offersionis fieri rogavi. Signum
                        +++++++ rnanibus <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Hugo/de Rocca">Ugo de <placeName ref="#places/2985"
                                    >Rocca</placeName></name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Beritius"
                            >Berizo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Balduinus">Balduino</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Rodelandus/de Verona"
                                >Rolando de <placeName ref="#places/59"
                            >Verona</placeName></name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Albertus/de Lusia">Albertus
                                de <placeName ref="#places/2986"
                        >Lusia</placeName></name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Liutulfus"
                            >Litulfus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes/Romano">Iohannes Romano</name></persName>
                        testes. (S.) Ego Adam notarius rogatus qui anc cartulam donationis
                        offersionis <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> dedi. Ego Fulco marchio dedi pro
                        ordinatione <rs key="#Testamentum">testamentum</rs> Garsende genitrice mea
                        terra in qua suprascripta cartula legitur. </ab>
                </div>
